ENTRY            F0571   20251215   20260305   20260305       F105
SUBENT        F0571001   20251215   20260305   20260305       F105
BIB                 11         27
TITLE      Angular distribution of proton non-Rutherford elastic
           scattering cross section of carbon and silicon
AUTHOR     (R.Salomonovic)
INSTITUTE  (3CZRCTI)
REFERENCE  (J,NIM/B,82,1,1993)
FACILITY   (VDG,3CZRCHU) Measurements were performed at several
           scattering angles: 120-170 degr. with Ep=1.660, 1.720,
           1.80 and 2.020 MeV
           (VDG,2AUSKUL) Measurements were performed at several
           scattering angles: 120-160 degr. with Ep=1.80, 2.0
           and 2.150 MeV in the case of silicon. In the case of
           carbon measurements were performed only at 1.80 MeV.
DETECTOR   (PS) PIPS detector which could be positioned
           to any laboratory scattering angle in the interval
           90-175 degr.
           (SIBAR)
REL-REF    (I,,M.Geretschlager+,J,PR/A,45,2842,1992) - Details
           of the experimental setup.
ERR-ANALYS (DATA-ERR,10.,20.) No information about source of
           uncertainty
COMMENT    The differences between two experiments (in Prague and
           in Linz) were less than 3 keV (energy shift) and
           4% (cross section values).
STATUS     (TABLE,,R.Salomonovic,J,NIM/B,82,1,1993) Tbl.1
HISTORY    (20030204C)
           (20251215U) SD: Small corrections in all Subents.
           DATA-ERR1/ERR2 -> DATA-ERR.
ENDBIB              27
NOCOMMON             0          0
ENDSUBENT           30
